name: VII. Peak
description:
Ascending into the third dimension freed us from the necessary collective.
With new opportunities each of us obtained free will. Everyone could follow wherever he wanted. We began to precieve the wordld from our own perspective.
This freedom immediately led to the firs difference of opinion in our history. The possibilities of 3D space were limitless, so we started building.
Thanks to φ, the greatest figures emerged. You might think that we have finally reached the end of our journey. However, very quickly, it turned out that freedom we recieved showed its destructive side.
